// P8.5 standard-library surface guardrail.
//
// Type-checking this file (via `nox check`) is the release-time assertion for
// PLAN 完成定义第 12 项后半 "标准库 fs/env/time/net/async/math/string/json/csv/tsv/array/map/option/result/process/path 最小入口".
// If any public stdlib surface is silently removed or its signature changes, the
// check step fails. The file is intentionally not executed: several entries
// require runtime capability grants, but `nox check` only resolves names and
// types, not capabilities.

